org.apache.flex.compiler.tree.metadata

Interface IMetaTagNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IASNode, IDecoration, IMetaInfo, ISourceLocation
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IAccessibilityTagNode, IDefaultPropertyTagNode, IEffectTagNode, IEventTagNode, IEventTriggerTagNode, IInspectableTagNode, IMultiValueMetaTagNode, IResourceBundleTagNode, IStyleTagNode, ITypedTagNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AccessibilityTagNode, AlternativeTagNode, BaseDefinitionMetaTagNode, BasicMetaTagNode, DefaultPropertyTagNode, EffectTagNode, EventTagNode, EventTriggerTagNode, InspectableTagNode, MetaTagNode, MultiValueMetaTagNode, ResourceBundleTagNode, SkinClassTagNode, StyleTagNode, TypedTagNode

    public interface IMetaTagNode
extends IASNode, IDecoration, IMetaInfo
    An AST node representing a single metadata annotation on a declaration.

    This node has no children.

    For example, 

     [Foo]
 [Bar]
 public var i:int;
    is represented as 
     IVariableNode
   IMetaTagsNode
     IMetaTagNode "Foo"
     IMetaTagNode "Bar"
   INamespaceDecorationNode "public"
   IKeywordNode "var"
   IIdentifierNode "i"
   IIdentifierNode "int"
